{"word":"H8092 - שִׁמְעָא - Shimʻâʼ - shim-aw' - Shimea","slug":"H8092","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׁמְעָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shimʻâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shim-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shimea"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁמעא</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>shim‛â'</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>shim-aw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Shimea = \"fame\" <ol><li>son of David by Bathsheba</li><li>brother of David, the 3rd son of Jesse<ol type='a'><li>also 'Shammah', 'Shimma', and 'Shimeah'</li></ol><li>a Gershonite Levite, father of Berachiah, and grandfather of Asaph</li><li>a Merarite Levite, son of Uzzah, and father of Haggiah</li></ol> <p />Origin: for <a href=\"#/H8093\">H8093</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2045\">H2045</a>, <a href=\"#/H3458\">H3458</a>, <a href=\"#/H3459\">H3459</a>, <a href=\"#/H3460\">H3460</a>, <a href=\"#/H4926\">H4926</a>, <a href=\"#/H4927\">H4927</a>, <a href=\"#/H4928\">H4928</a>, <a href=\"#/H8051\">H8051</a>, <a href=\"#/H8052\">H8052</a>, <a href=\"#/H8085\">H8085</a>, <a href=\"#/H8087\">H8087</a>, <a href=\"#/H8088\">H8088</a>, <a href=\"#/H8089\">H8089</a>, <a href=\"#/H8090\">H8090</a>, <a href=\"#/H8091\">H8091</a>, <a href=\"#/H8093\">H8093</a>, <a href=\"#/H8094\">H8094</a>, <a href=\"#/H8095\">H8095</a>, <a href=\"#/H8096\">H8096</a>, <a href=\"#/H8097\">H8097</a>, <a href=\"#/H8098\">H8098</a>, <a href=\"#/H8099\">H8099</a>, <a href=\"#/H8100\">H8100</a>, <a href=\"#/H8101\">H8101</a>"}]}